Today we lost a true legend @frenchycannoli 
 
Frenchy was a kind-hearted, passionate, and beautiful man. He cared about the craft of creating the world’s best hashish and he cared even more about people. 

Frenchy will live on in the people he helped and the education he brought to the world. 

RIP Frenchy. We love you and we’re grateful for you ❤️ 🕊
